data.description: Well maintained ranch on over .5 acres in quiet Durham community close to parks, Duke University and top-rated schools. Turnkey property is ready for you, with newly finished hardwoods, fresh paint and several flexible spaces for hobbies, work or extra bedroom plus ample parking- private 4-car driveway and street parking. Spacious, level side yard for all kinds of recreation. Benefit from years of improvements and renovations including new roof (2020), Trane HVAC (2019), all new Andersen energy efficient windows (2017), complete French drainage system and gutters, (2016), encapsulated crawl space (2016) and Rinnai tankless hot-water heater. Enjoy a formal living room, dining room and family room with a cozy wood-burning fireplace. 3 bedrooms plus extra bedroom/flex space with additional Champion patio/sun room and brick patio. Wooded corner lot with ample parking and 3 additional sheds plus lean-to open storage area. Spacious front porch with room for rocking chairs. Great opportunity!
